==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Randomize
<hw>Ran"dom*ize</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To arrange or rearrange so
that there is no predetermined order; to make random; to select by a
random process; to assign (members of a group) into subgroups by a
random process.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> make random.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Randomly</ent>⟦br⟧
